# Copy values into Render / Vercel dashboards (do not commit secrets).

# --- Easiest demo (laptop only, one tunnel) ---
# 1) ollama serve   (and pull your model)
# 2) cd frontend && npm run demo:sync
# 3) cd ../backend && uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000
# 4) cloudflared tunnel --url http://127.0.0.1:8000   (or ngrok http 8000)
# 5) Open the printed https URL; add that origin in Privy dashboard.
# Ollama stays on localhost — no second tunnel. backend/static/ is gitignored.

# --- Render (backend) ---
# OLLAMA_URL=https://your-tunnel.trycloudflare.com/api/chat
# OLLAMA_MODEL=llama3
# CONTRACT_ADDRESS=0x...
# CORS_ORIGINS=https://your-app.vercel.app
# (omit CORS_ORIGINS or set to * for wide-open demo CORS)

# --- Vercel (frontend build) ---
# VITE_API_URL=https://bitbrain-api.onrender.com
# VITE_PRIVY_APP_ID=...
# VITE_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=0x...
# VITE_ACCESS_READ_RPC=https://ethereum-sepolia-rpc.publicnode.com
